<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<title>Acme Cloud — realistic multi-feature page</title>
<style>
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  body { margin: 0; font-family: sans-serif; color: #222222; background: #f4f6fb; }

  /* ---- top NAV BAR: flex row of links + a right-aligned button ---- */
  /* LOUD NAVY band so a framebuffer scan can find the bar across the top. */
  nav { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 20px;
        background: #10203a; padding: 12px 20px; }
  nav .brand { color: #ffffff; font-weight: bold; font-size: 18px; }
  nav a { color: #cdd6e6; text-decoration: none; }
  nav .spacer { flex: 1; }
  /* right-aligned CTA button, LOUD ORANGE. */
  nav .cta { background: #ff5500; color: #ffffff; padding: 8px 16px;
             border: none; border-radius: 4px; }

  .wrap { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
  h1 { font-size: 28px; margin: 12px 0 8px 0; }
  p.body { line-height: 1.5; margin: 8px 0; }
  a.inline { color: #1155cc; }

  /* ---- 3-column CARD GRID (each card: heading + text + colored box) ---- */
  .cards { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
  .card { flex: 1; background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #d0d6e2;
          border-radius: 6px; padding: 14px; }
  .card h3 { margin: 0 0 6px 0; font-size: 16px; }
  .card p { margin: 0 0 10px 0; font-size: 13px; color: #555555; }
  /* Each card's colored box is a distinct LOUD colour so a pixel scan can tell
     whether the three cards laid out side-by-side (columns) or stacked. */
  .swatch { height: 46px; border-radius: 4px; }
  .s1 { background: #e6194b; }   /* crimson  */
  .s2 { background: #3cb44b; }   /* green    */
  .s3 { background: #009999; }   /* teal (kept clear of the blue DE wallpaper) */

  /* ---- simple TABLE with cell borders ---- */
  table { border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 20px 0; }
  th, td { border: 1px solid #444444; padding: 8px 10px; text-align: left; }
  thead th { background: #ffe119; }   /* LOUD YELLOW header row */

  /* ---- lists ---- */
  .lists { display: flex; gap: 40px; }
  ol, ul { margin: 8px 0; padding-left: 22px; line-height: 1.5; }

  /* ---- blockquote ---- */
  blockquote { margin: 20px 0; padding: 10px 16px;
               border-left: 6px solid #911eb4;   /* LOUD PURPLE accent bar */
               background: #ffffff; color: #333333; font-style: italic; }

  /* ---- form ---- */
  form { background: #ffffff; border: 1px solid #d0d6e2; border-radius: 6px;
         padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0; }
  label { display: block; margin: 8px 0 4px 0; font-size: 13px; }
  input[type=text] { width: 260px; padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #888888;
                     border-radius: 4px; }
  select { padding: 8px; border: 1px solid #888888; border-radius: 4px; }
  button.submit { margin-top: 12px; background: #f032e6; color: #ffffff;
                  border: none; padding: 10px 18px; border-radius: 4px; }

  footer { background: #10203a; color: #cdd6e6; padding: 16px 20px;
           margin-top: 24px; }

  /* ---- Wikipedia-style float:right INFOBOX: a bordered, uniformly SHADED
     panel the body text wraps to the left of. LOUD-ish light steel background
     (#c8dcf0) so a framebuffer scan / eyeball can confirm the WHOLE box fills
     one uniform colour (not patchy per-cell shading with white gutters). */
  table.infobox { float: right; width: 220px; margin: 0 0 12px 16px;
                  border: 1px solid #6a7fa0; background-color: #c8dcf0; }
  table.infobox th { text-align: center; font-weight: bold; padding: 6px; }
  table.infobox td { padding: 4px 6px; }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <nav>
    <span class="brand">AcmeCloud</span>
    <a href="#features">Features</a>
    <a href="#pricing">Pricing</a>
    <a href="#docs">Docs</a>
    <span class="spacer"></span>
    <button class="cta">Sign up</button>
  </nav>

  <div class="wrap">
    <h1>Ship faster with AcmeCloud</h1>
    <table class="infobox">
      <tr><th colspan="2">AcmeCloud</th></tr>
      <tr><td>Type</td><td>Platform</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Founded</td><td>2021</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Regions</td><td>Global</td></tr>
      <tr><td>Uptime</td><td>99.99%</td></tr>
    </table>
    <p class="body">AcmeCloud is a managed platform for building and deploying
       modern applications. This lead wraps across a few lines to exercise
       line-box layout and inline flow. Read the
       <a class="inline" href="#docs">documentation</a> to get started.</p>

    <div class="cards">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Compute</h3>
        <p>Elastic virtual machines that scale on demand.</p>
        <div class="swatch s1"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Storage</h3>
        <p>Durable object storage with global replication.</p>
        <div class="swatch s2"></div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Network</h3>
        <p>Low-latency edge delivery across regions.</p>
        <div class="swatch s3"></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>Plan</th><th>vCPUs</th><th>Price</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Starter</td><td>2</td><td>$10/mo</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Pro</td><td>8</td><td>$40/mo</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Scale</td><td>32</td><td>$160/mo</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <div class="lists">
      <div>
        <h3>Getting started</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Create an account</li>
          <li>Provision a project</li>
          <li>Deploy your app</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3>Includes</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Automatic backups</li>
          <li>Global CDN</li>
          <li>24/7 support</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <blockquote>"AcmeCloud cut our deploy time in half." — a happy customer</blockquote>

    <form>
      <label for="email">Work email</label>
      <input type="text" id="email" name="email" value="you@example.com">
      <label for="plan">Choose a plan</label>
      <select id="plan" name="plan">
        <option>Starter</option>
        <option>Pro</option>
        <option>Scale</option>
      </select>
      <div><button class="submit" type="submit">Request demo</button></div>
    </form>

    <p class="body">Logo: <img src="sample.png" width="96" height="64" alt="logo"></p>
  </div>

  <footer>&copy; 2026 AcmeCloud, Inc. &middot; All rights reserved.</footer>
</body>
</html>
